#

Mushroom and Spinach Salad

10 min
$8.5
250 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-FreeLow-Calorie

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Salad

Tags:

SaladHealthyQuickFresh

Description

A refreshing and earthy salad featuring fresh mushrooms and spinach, tossed with a light dressing for a healthy meal.

Ingredients

  • fresh spinach: 3 cups
  • mixed mushrooms (e.g., button, cremini): 1 cup
  • cherry tomatoes: 1 cup
  • cucumber: 1 medium
  • avocado: 1 medium
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • balsamic vinegar: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • garlic powder: 1/2 teaspoon
